title: 116: NFL Week 1 Preview
itunes:title: 116: NFL Week 1 Preview
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks get you ready for kickoff by breaking down the biggest storyline surrounding each match-up. The guys then pick the biggest games this weekend in the NFL and College Football.
